<div dir="ltr">Hi,<div><br></div><div>KNEM can improve the performance significantly for intra-node communication and that&#39;s why MXM is using it.</div><div>If you don&#39;t want to use it, you can suppress this warning by adding the following to your command line after mpirun:</div>

<div>-x MXM_LOG_LEVEL=error</div><div><br></div><div>Alina. </div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Wed, Aug 27, 2014 at 4:28 PM, Brock Palen <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:brockp@umich.edu" target="_blank">brockp@umich.edu</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>
